comment: Mahinmi (IND) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Bryant's (LAL) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Indiana should be awarded possession is upheld.
Clarkson (LAL) makes contact with George's (IND) arm, affecting his shot attempt.
Randle (LAL) and Mahinmi (IND) briefly engage and separate while rebounding.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that LAL should be awarded possession was overturned and possession given to IND.
George (IND) gathers on his right foot and lands simultaneously on both feet before elevating for his shot.
Bass (LA) makes contact to the body of George (IND) that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Mahinmi (IND) and Black (LAL) briefly engage and separate while rebounding.
Clarkson (LAL) commits the take foul on Ellis (IND).
Randle (LAL) commits the take foul of George (IND).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the shot was taken before the clock reached 00:00 was upheld.
